OL,3,CWife 'in tears' as season ticket
OL,4,Ctransfer turned down after husband's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FA grieving mother whose late husband
OL,8,Fwas a lifelong Manchester United fan
OL,9,Fsays she is "beyond disappointed"
OL,10,Fafter the club refused to change his
OL,11,Fseason ticket into her name so she
OL,12,Fcould continue to visit with her son.
OL,14,FJane McLaughlin lost her husband Rob
OL,15,Ffollowing a short illness during the
OL,16,FCovid-19 lockdown in 2020.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
