OL,3,CWife 'in tears' as season ticket
OL,4,Ctransfer turned down after husband's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FHe had held a season ticket at Old
OL,8,FTrafford for more than 25 years -
OL,9,Fearning his place as a platinum ticket
OL,10,Fholder and giving him access to away
OL,11,Fgame tickets as well as a plaque on a
OL,12,Fseat at the stadium.
OL,14,FFollowing his death, Jane said she
OL,15,Finitially did not change the ticket
OL,16,Finto her name to continue attending
OL,17,Fthe games with her son Robbie, who is
OL,18,Falso a keen supporter of Manchester
OL,19,FUnited.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
