OL,3,CWife 'in tears' as season ticket
OL,4,Ctransfer turned down after husband's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FShe now claims, after she recently
OL,8,Fattempted to have the ticket changed
OL,9,Finto her name, the club denied it,
OL,10,Fdespite an appeal.
OL,12,FJane says she is "beyond disappointed"
OL,13,Fand even had to leave work in tears
OL,14,Fafter being informed of the outcome of
OL,15,Fthe appeal saying it was "like a
OL,16,Fsecondary loss".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
