OL,7,FShe said her only option now is to
OL,8,Flose the loyalty status and join a
OL,9,Fwaiting list for season tickets -
OL,10,Fmeaning she is unable to apply for
OL,11,Faway game tickets and her son, now 14,
OL,12,Fwould be expected to attend games on
OL,13,Fhis own.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
