OL,7,FIt is understood that although the
OL,8,Fclub understands Jane's perspective
OL,9,Fand regrets the disappointment felt by
OL,10,Fher, they have to apply ticket
OL,11,Fpolicies "consistently" for the
OL,12,F"benefit of all supporters" and
OL,13,Fhundreds of others in the same
OL,14,Fposition.
OL,16,FThis is also due to the thousands of
OL,17,Ffans currently on the Manchester
OL,18,FUnited season ticket waiting list.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
