OL,4,Ctransfer turned down after husband's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"The reason this came about this
OL,8,Fseason was because, for the first
OL,9,Ftime, United started asking for photo
OL,10,FID to renew season tickets, including
OL,11,Fa photo from passport or ID and a
OL,12,Fselfie that all need to match the name
OL,13,Fof the ticket.
OL,15,F"I did ask previously for a name
OL,16,Fchange a few years ago. But at the
OL,17,Ftime they didn't make it clear it was
OL,18,Fmy only opportunity to take it, and
OL,19,Fthey said I'd lose the loyalty which
OL,20,Fwould mean I couldn't apply for away
OL,21,Ftickets.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
