OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F396A1744398021
OL,3,CWife 'in tears' as season ticket
OL,4,Ctransfer turned down after husband's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"He was also a platinum holder meaning
OL,8,Fhe also got a plaque which, for me, is
OL,9,Fextremely poignant made and makes me
OL,10,Ffeel like he is still a part of it,
OL,11,Flike some sort of memorial. It meant
OL,12,Fso much to him.
OL,14,F"My son is 14 now and has his own
OL,15,Fseason ticket. But he'd have to go on
OL,16,Fhis own, with adults sitting beside
OL,17,Fhim who he doesn't know. But it's also
OL,18,Fabout me not getting the chance to
OL,19,Fcontinue making memories with him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
