OL,3,CWife 'in tears' as season ticket
OL,4,Ctransfer turned down after husband's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"Nobody expects to lose their dad at
OL,8,Fjust 10 years old. It's been a really
OL,9,Ftough few years for us as a family,
OL,10,Fand I've been taking him back to the
OL,11,Fmatches ever since they continued
OL,12,Fafter the pandemic."
OL,14,FAfter first being told that she would
OL,15,Flose the season ticket, Jane says she
OL,16,Fthen appealed the decision but was
OL,17,Ftold it had also been rejected.
OL,19,FIt is understood the club say this is
OL,20,Fso there is consistency in their
OL,21,Fticket policies across the board.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
