OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F396A1744398021
OL,3,CWife 'in tears' as season ticket
OL,4,Ctransfer turned down after husband's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"I am beyond disappointed. It's so
OL,8,Fmuch more than that. I received a call
OL,9,Ffrom the club telling me my appeal had
OL,10,Fbeen rejected. I was so upset it
OL,11,Ftriggered a huge wave of grief and I
OL,12,Fhad to go home from work in tears,"
OL,13,FJane said.
OL,15,F"Unless somebody has been through a
OL,16,Fsimilar level of grief you can't
OL,17,Fexplain how it can hit you. This now
OL,18,Fjust feels like a secondary loss.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
