OL,3,CWife 'in tears' as season ticket
OL,4,Ctransfer turned down after husband's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"But, I'm not surprised by the club.
OL,8,FThe people that make these decisions
OL,9,Fare faceless. Where is the kindness,
OL,10,Fhumanity and empathy? They are only
OL,11,Fthinking from a business side and not
OL,12,Fthe human side.
OL,14,F"This is my opportunity to spend time
OL,15,Fwith my son, and to keep his dad's
OL,16,Fmemory alive. Most of his memories of
OL,17,Fhis dad are from matches. He can still
OL,18,Fremember the last one he went to with
OL,19,Fhis dad. So, it's not just about the
OL,20,Ftickets."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
