OL,7,FEarlier this year, United introduced
OL,8,FID verification, explaining the move
OL,9,Fwas an attempt to tackle ticket
OL,10,Ftouting at Old Trafford.
OL,12,FTheir ID will then be cross-referenced
OL,13,Fagainst the name and date of birth on
OL,14,Fthe club's system for the season
OL,15,Fticket.
